oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Original wills, Autin, Frances R., 1918 November 15
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An original will of Frances R. Autin, “widow of William T. Autin,” dated October 21st, 1915. Illustrates the first page of the document. Autin’s will was presented for probate to the Davidson County Court on November 15th, 1918. Forms part of Record Group 16, Original Wills, 1780-1925.
